t4.Board

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • t4.Board.Cell

  • public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
    A Cell represents one square on a t4 board. It is identified by an index for both the row and column of the Cell. Only one Player is allowed to play in a Cell for a given Board.
    Author:
    Teddy
